How to install:

1. Prepare runtime - you can use simple tomcat server or SAP Java Web Tomcat 7 runtime - download at: https://tools.hana.ondemand.com
2. Download Eclipse Java EE edition
3. Install SAP Java Web Tomcat 7 tools - update site can be found again on: https://tools.hana.ondemand.com (install only tools for java)
4. Import projects into eclipse

Next you can run the application locally or in the cloud. You can use a free hanatrial account from: https://hanatrial.ondemand.com
